title.narrative: MULTILATORGANISATION and P0301 for Strengthening PFM II

description.narrative: This activity (MULTILATORGANISATION and P0301 for Strengthening PFM II) is a component of STRENGTHENING Public Financial Management II reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Multilateral organisation' and a budget of £4,999,828. This component benefits Kyrgyzstan, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Public finance management (PFM), Decentralisation and support to subnational government, Democratic participation and civil society. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, International Bank for Reconstruction and Development, International Bank for Reconstruction and Development (IBRD), Switzerland - Swiss Agency for Development and Cooperation (SDC), World Bank, The. The start date is 01-01-2009 and the end date is 20-09-2016.
